fake its GDP data.

108
00:05:15,810 --> 00:05:18,900
What’s interesting about the $200 billion
number

109
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:23,039
is that China doesn’t import that much from
the US.

110
00:05:23,039 --> 00:05:26,290
So while they can match a 50 billion dollar
tariff,

111
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:29,970
they can’t match a 200 billion dollar one.

112
00:05:29,970 --> 00:05:31,360
What they could do instead

113
